@startuml AirQualitySystemArchitecture
!theme plain

title KIẾN TRÚC HỆ THỐNG GIÁM SÁT CHẤT LƯỢNG KHÔNG KHÍ

' === STYLES ===
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam roundcorner 8

' === LAYERS ===
rectangle "Layer 1: Thiết bị đo" <<device>> #LightBlue
rectangle "Layer 2: Truyền dữ liệu" <<transmission>> #LightGreen
rectangle "Layer 3: Backend (Go)" <<backend>> #LightYellow
rectangle "Layer 4: ML Service (Python)" <<ml>> #LightPink
rectangle "Layer 5: Frontend (React)" <<frontend>> #LightCyan

' === LAYER 1: DEVICE LAYER ===
package "Layer 1: Thiết bị đo" {
  [ESP32 Sensor Node] as ESP32
  [Cảm biến đo PM1.0\nPM2.5, PM10] as PM_SENSOR
  [Cảm biến nhiệt độ\n& độ ẩm] as DHT_SENSOR
  [Công tắc cảnh báo\nngưỡng] as THRESHOLD_SW
}

ESP32 --> PM_SENSOR : Serial
ESP32 --> DHT_SENSOR : Serial
PM_SENSOR ..> THRESHOLD_SW : Ngưỡng WHO
DHT_SENSOR ..> THRESHOLD_SW : Ngưỡng WHO

' === MQTT BROKER ===
package "Layer 2: Truyền dữ liệu" {
  [MQTT Broker\n(Mosquitto:1883)] as MQTT_BROKER
  [Telegraf\n(MQTT Consumer)] as TELEGRAF
  [InfluxDB Cloud\n(HTTPS API)] as INFLUXDB

  MQTT_BROKER --> TELEGRAF : MQTT (TCP)
  TELEGRAF --> INFLUXDB : Line Protocol (HTTPS)
}

ESP32 --> MQTT_BROKER : MQTT
ESP32 <--> THRESHOLD_SW : Cảnh báo local

' === INFLUXDB DATA STRUCTURE ===
note bottom of INFLUXDB
**Measurement:** sensor_data
**Tags:** sensor_node, location, host, topic
**Fields:** pm1, pm25, pm10, temperature, humidity, heat_index, aqi, comfort
end note

' === BACKEND LAYER ===
package "Layer 3: Backend (Go:8088)" {
  [RealtimePoller\n(30s interval)] as POLLER
  [WebSocketService] as WS_SERVICE
  [InfluxService] as INFLUX_SERVICE
  [AlertService] as ALERT_SERVICE
  [MLService] as ML_CLIENT

  [REST API\n(Gin Framework)] as REST_API

  database "PostgreSQL\n(Metadata)" as POSTGRES {
    [users]
    [sensors]
    [alerts]
    [settings]
    [sessions]
  }
}

INFLUXDB --> INFLUX_SERVICE : Query API
INFLUX_SERVICE --> POLLER : Latest data
POLLER --> WS_SERVICE : Broadcast
POLLER --> ALERT_SERVICE : Check threshold
ALERT_SERVICE --> POSTGRES : Save alerts
INFLUX_SERVICE --> REST_API : Query data
ML_CLIENT --> REST_API : Forecast
WS_SERVICE --> REST_API : Real-time

' === REST API ENDPOINTS ===
note right of REST_API
**Endpoints:**
- /v1/auth/* - Authentication
- /v1/data/* - InfluxDB queries
- /v1/forecast/* - ML forecasting
- /v1/alerts/* - Alert management
- /v1/sensors/* - Sensor CRUD
- /v1/settings/* - Configuration
- /v1/ws/realtime - WebSocket
end note

' === ML SERVICE ===
package "Layer 4: ML Service (Python:8000)" {
  [FastAPI Server] as FASTAPI
  [LSTM Model] as LSTM_MODEL
  [GRU Model] as GRU_MODEL
  [BiLSTM Model] as BILSTM_MODEL
  [Informer Model] as INFORMER_MODEL
  [ARIMA Model] as ARIMA_MODEL

  [Drift Monitoring\n(PSI-based)] as DRIFT_MON

  FASTAPI --> LSTM_MODEL : predict
  FASTAPI --> GRU_MODEL : predict
  FASTAPI --> BILSTM_MODEL : predict
  FASTAPI --> INFORMER_MODEL : predict
  FASTAPI --> ARIMA_MODEL : predict

  LSTM_MODEL ..> DRIFT_MON : monitor
  GRU_MODEL ..> DRIFT_MON : monitor
  BILSTM_MODEL ..> DRIFT_MON : monitor
  INFORMER_MODEL ..> DRIFT_MON : monitor
}

ML_CLIENT ..> FASTAPI : HTTP POST /forecast
FASTAPI ..> DRIFT_MON : track drift

' === FRONTEND LAYER ===
package "Layer 5: Frontend (React:5173)" {
  [useWebSocket Hook] as WS_HOOK
  [useApi Hooks\n(React Query)] as API_HOOKS

  [Dashboard\n(Index.tsx)] as DASHBOARD
  [KpiCard] as KPI
  [PMChart] as PM_CHART
  [AqiGauge] as AQI_GAUGE
  [Heatmap] as HEATMAP
  [ForecastTable] as FORECAST_TABLE
  [DriftTrackingSection] as DRIFT_UI

  [Pages:\nLocations, Alerts\nSettings, Reports] as OTHER_PAGES
}

WS_HOOK --> DASHBOARD : Realtime data
API_HOOKS --> DASHBOARD : REST API
DASHBOARD --> KPI : display
DASHBOARD --> PM_CHART : display
DASHBOARD --> AQI_GAUGE : display
DASHBOARD --> HEATMAP : display
DASHBOARD --> FORECAST_TABLE : ML forecast
DASHBOARD --> DRIFT_UI : drift status
DASHBOARD --> OTHER_PAGES : navigation

' === CONNECTIONS ===
REST_API -up-> WS_HOOK : WSS
REST_API -up-> API_HOOKS : HTTPS

' === DATA FLOW ARROWS ===
note as N1
**Luồng dữ liệu chính:**
1. ESP32 gửi JSON qua MQTT → Broker
2. Telegraf parse → InfluxDB line protocol
3. InfluxDB lưu time-series data
4. RealtimePoller (30s) → QueryLatest
5. Broadcast WebSocket → Frontend
6. AlertService kiểm tra ngưỡng → PostgreSQL
7. User request forecast → ML API → Response
end note

' === LEGEND ===
legend bottom right
  | Màu | Lớp |
  | <back:#LightBlue>   </back> | Thiết bị đo |
  | <back:#LightGreen>  </back> | Truyền dữ liệu |
  | <back:#LightYellow> </back> | Backend (Go) |
  | <back:#LightPink>   </back> | ML Service (Python) |
  | <back:#LightCyan>   </back> | Frontend (React) |
end legend

@enduml